/a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The theorems in a simp set.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheorems","kind":"structure","line":596,"name":"Lean.Meta.SimpTheorems","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L596-L610"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheoremTree\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimpTheoremTree</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheoremTree","kind":"def","line":594,"name":"Lean.Meta.SimpTheoremTree","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L594-L594"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.mkSimpEntryOfDeclToUnfold\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkSimpEntryOfDeclToUnfold</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpEntry\">SimpEntry</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given the name of a declaration to unfold, return the `SimpEntry` (or entries) that\nimplement this unfolding, using either the equational theorems, or `SimpEntry.toUnfold`, or both.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.mkSimpEntryOfDeclToUnfold","kind":"def","line":555,"name":"Lean.Meta.mkSimpEntryOfDeclToUnfold","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L555-L591"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.unfoldEvenWithEqns\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">unfoldEvenWithEqns</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Even if a function has equation theorems,\nwe also store it in the `toUnfold` set in the following two cases:\n1- It was defined by structural recursion and has a smart-unfolding associated declaration.\n2- It is non-recursive.\n\nReason: `unfoldPartialApp := true` or conditional equations may not apply.\n\nRemark: In the future, we are planning to disable this\nbehavior unless `unfoldPartialApp := true`.\nMoreover, users will have to use `f.eq_def` if they want to force the definition to be\nunfolded.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.unfoldEvenWithEqns","kind":"def","line":537,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.unfoldEvenWithEqns","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L537-L553"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.ignoreEquations\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Simp</span>.<span class=\"name\">ignoreEquations</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">declName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/CoreM.html#Lean.Core.CoreM\">CoreM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Reducible functions and projection functions should always be put in `toUnfold`, instead\nof trying to use equational theorems.\n\nThe simplifiers has special support for structure and class projections, and gets\nconfused when they suddenly rewrite, so ignore equations for them\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.Simp.ignoreEquations","kind":"def","line":527,"name":"Lean.Meta.Simp.ignoreEquations","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L527-L535"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.instInhabitedSimpEntry\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">instInhabitedSimpEntry</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpEntry\">SimpEntry</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.instInhabitedSimpEntry","kind":"instance","line":525,"name":"Lean.Meta.instInhabitedSimpEntry","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L525-L525"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpEntry.toUnfoldThms\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimpEntry</span>.<span class=\"name\">toUnfoldThms</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a></span> → <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpEntry\">SimpEntry</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpEntry.toUnfoldThms","kind":"ctor","line":524,"name":"Lean.Meta.SimpEntry.toUnfoldThms","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L524-L524"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpEntry.toUnfold\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimpEntry</span>.<span class=\"name\">toUnfold</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a> → <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpEntry\">SimpEntry</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.htm