Rfl` is true if `proof` is by a `@[backward_defeq]` theorem (i.e. rfl at default,\nbut not instance, transparency). Honored by `dsimp` only when\n`backward.defeqAttrib.useBackward` is set.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem.backwardRfl","kind":"def","line":182,"name":"Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem.backwardRfl","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L182-L182"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem.rfl\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimpTheorem</span>.<span class=\"name\">rfl</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem\">SimpTheorem</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`rfl` is true if `proof` is by `Eq.refl`, `rfl` or a `@[defeq]` theorem.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem.rfl","kind":"def","line":176,"name":"Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem.rfl","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L176-L176"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem.origin\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimpTheorem</span>.<span class=\"name\">origin</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"