pr</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.Origin\">Lean.Meta.Origin</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> → <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem\">Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem</a></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem.mk","kind":"ctor","line":146,"name":"Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L146-L183"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimpTheorem</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The fields `levelParams` and `proof` are used to encode the proof of the simp theorem.\nIf the `proof` is a global declaration `c`, we store `Expr.const c []` at `proof` without the universe levels, and `levelParams` is set to `#[]`\nWhen using the lemma, we create fresh universe metavariables.\nMotivation: most simp theorems are global declarations, and this approach is faster and saves memory.\n\nThe field `levelParams` is not empty only when we elaborate an expression provided by the user, and it contains universe metavariables.\nThen, we use `abstractMVars` to abstract the universe metavariables and create new fresh universe parameters that are stored at the field `levelParams`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem","kind":"structure","line":146,"name":"Lean.Meta.SimpTheorem","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L146-L183"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheoremKey\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">SimpTheoremKey</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.SimpTheoremKey","kind":"def","line":144,"name":"Lean.Meta.SimpTheoremKey","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L144-L144"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.instDecidableLtOrigin\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">instDecidableLtOrigin</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">a </span><span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.Origin\">Origin</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Decidable\">Decidable</a> (<span class=\"fn\">a</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LT.lt\">&lt;</a> <span class=\"fn\">b</span>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.instDecidableLtOrigin","kind"