pan><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Inhabited\">Inhabited</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.Origin\">Origin</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.instInhabitedOrigin","kind":"instance","line":91,"name":"Lean.Meta.instInhabitedOrigin","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L91-L91"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.Origin.other\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Origin</span>.<span class=\"name\">other</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">name</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.Origin\">Origin</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Some other origin. `name` should not collide with the other types\nfor erasure to work correctly, and simp trace will ignore this lemma.\nThe other origins should be preferred if possible.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.Origin.other","kind":"ctor","line":85,"name":"Lean.Meta.Origin.other","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.lean#L85-L90"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Simp/SimpTheorems.html#Lean.Meta.Origin.stx\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Origin</span>.<span class=\"nam